OL,7,FAdverts for three supplements brands
OL,8,Fthat claimed to help treat conditions
OL,9,Fincluding autism and ADHD have been
OL,10,Fbanned.
OL,12,FA paid-for Facebook ad in April for
OL,13,FAspire Nutrition said: "The secret
OL,14,Fweapon parents of ASD kids swear by",
OL,15,Fwhile a review attributed to "Tara K.
OL,16,FVerified Buyer", said "This has helped
OL,17,Fmy 5 year old with Level 2 autism so
OL,18,Fmuch."
