OL,7,FAnd a third paid-for Facebook ad for
OL,8,FSpectrum Awakening stated: "My five-
OL,9,Fyear-old son Scout is diagnosed with
OL,10,Freceptive expressive language disorder
OL,11,Fand sensory disorder. Until I found
OL,12,FSpectrum Awakening he could barely put
OL,13,Fa sentence together with very limited
OL,14,Fspeech and words and lots of jargon."
OL,16,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,17,F(ASA) investigated all three ads over
OL,18,Fwhether the claims that each
OL,19,Fsupplement could help to prevent or
OL,20,Fcure autism, was in breach of
OL,21,Fregulations.
