OL,7,FAspire Nutrition said that on being
OL,8,Finformed of the complaint, they had
OL,9,Fstopped ads being sent to UK residents
OL,10,Fwho visited their website and had
OL,11,Fwithdrawn the ad entirely for all
OL,12,Faudiences.
OL,14,FDrop Supplements said their ads
OL,15,Ffeaturing Happy Mind made no direct or
OL,16,Fimplied statements about curing,
OL,17,Ftreating or preventing ailments or
OL,18,Fdiseases.
